         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065">
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iustitia et iudicio Dei</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P" n="16"/>De <sic>caritate</sic> seu dilectione et 
              ho<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="17"/>diositate dei ad hominem: ca: viii
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e118">Iob hystoria. ca. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e125" source="http://scta.info/resource/iob11_6@15-23">multa dona exegeris a domino
               <lb ed="#P" n="19"/>quae meretur iniquitas tua.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#P" n="20"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e132">Psamista. pslamus. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e137" source="http://scta.info/resource/ps5_7@1-5">odisti omnes qui operantur iniquitatem
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/>virum sanguinum: et delosum abhominabitur
               <lb ed="#P" n="22"/>deus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#P" n="23"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e151">Idem xxxiii. pslamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e154" source="http://scta.info/resource/Ipetr3_12@2-11">Oculi domini super iustos: et aures 
               <lb ed="#P" n="24"/>eius in praeces eorum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e162">
              <lb ed="#P" n="25"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e164">Idem. psalmus. lxxxiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e164" source="http://scta.info/resource/ps83_12@2-6">Misericordiam et veritatem diligit deus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e170">
              <lb ed="#P" n="26"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e174">Idem clxvi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e172">dominis diligit iustos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e184">Salomon in prouer. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e180" source="http://scta.info/resource/prov6_16@1-10 http://scta.info/resource/prov6_17@1-8 http://scta.info/resource/prov6_18@1-10 http://scta.info/resource/prov6_19@1-11">Sex sunt quodit dominis
               <lb ed="#P" n="28"/>et septimus detestatur ania eius. Oculos subli
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="29"/>mes linguam mendacem manum effundentis in
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="30"/>noxium sanguinem. Cor machinans cogitationes
               <lb ed="#P" n="31"/>peximas. Pedes Veloces ad currem deum ad malum
               <lb ed="#P" n="32"/>preferentem mendaciam testem fallacem: et eum
               <lb ed="#P" n="33"/>qui inter fratres feminat discordias.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e197">
               <lb ed="#P" n="34"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e207">Ibidem. v. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e201" source="http://scta.info/resource/prov15_9@6-11">qui sequitur iustitiam diligitur a domino</quote>
            </p> 
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e206"><!--combined with above-->
               <lb ed="#P" n="35"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e210" source="http://scta.info/resource/prov15_26@1-4">abboiatio domini cogitationes male:</quote>
            </p> 
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e214"><!--combined with above-->
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e216" source="http://scta.info/resource/prov15_29@1-9">longe est dominis
               <lb ed="#P" n="36"/>ab impiis: et orationes iustorum exaudiet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e224">
               <lb ed="#P" n="37"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e234">Ibidem. ca. vii</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e226" source="http://scta.info/resource/prov17_15@1-12">Qui iustificat impium: et
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="38"/>condemnat iustum abominabilis est vterque 
               <lb ed="#P" n="39"/>apud deum.</quote>
            </p> 
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e232">
               <lb ed="#P" n="40"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e246">Ezechiel propheta. ca. xviii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e236" source="http://scta.info/resource/ez18_23@1-18">Nuquid voluntatis
               <lb ed="#P" n="41"/>meae est mors impii dicit dominus deus: et
               <lb ed="#P" n="42"/>non ut conuertatur a viis suis: et viuat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e244">
               <lb ed="#P" n="43"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e258">Idem xxxiii</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e246" source="http://scta.info/resource/ez33_11@9-20">Nolo mortem impii: sed ut con
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="44"/>uertatur impius a via sua mala et vivat</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e254">
               <lb ed="#P" n="45"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e272"><sic>Regum iii. ca. xiii.</sic><!--This is 2 Samuel 14, and 3 Kings does not exist--></ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e258" source="http://scta.info/resource/IIsam14_14@12-25">Non vult deus perire animam
               <lb ed="#P" n="46"/>sed retractat cogitans ne penitus pereat
               <lb ed="#P" n="47"/>qui ablectus est. </quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e267">
               <lb ed="#P" n="48"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e287">Tullius in oratione pro quinto ligario.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e271">homies ad
               <lb ed="#P" n="49"/>deos nulla re propius eradunt quam salutem
               <lb ed="#P" n="50"/>hominibus dando.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e279">
               <lb ed="#P" n="51"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e301">Ioannes in apocalipsi. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e283" source="http://scta.info/resource/ap3_20@2-24">ait dominis. Sto adhost
               <lb ed="#P" n="52"/>tium: et pulso siquis audierit vocem meam:
               <lb ed="#P" n="53"/>et aperuerit introibo ad illum: et cenabo cum
               <lb ed="#P" n="54"/>eo et ille mecum.</quote>  
            </p> 
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e293">
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e315">Idem in evangeli. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e295" source="http://scta.info/resource/io3_16@1-22 http://scta.info/resource/io3_17@1-17">Sic dilexit deus mun
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="56"/>dum ut filium suum vnigenitum daret ut
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/>omnis: qui credit in illum non pereat sed habeat vitam
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/><sic>etternam</sic>. Non enim misit deus filium suum
               <lb ed="#P" n="59"/>in <sic>humanae</sic><!--Humanae is not in the original--> mundum: ut iudicet mundum: sed
               <lb ed="#P" n="60"/>ut saluetur mundus per ipsum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e309">
               <lb ed="#P" n="61"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e333">Ibidem xv. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e311" source="http://scta.info/resource/io15_10@1-8">Ait yesus si precepta mea ser
               <lb ed="#P" break="no" n="62"/>uaueritis manebitis in dilectione mea</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e325">
               OMITTED 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e337">&gt;
               <lb ed="#P" n="63"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e367">Paulus ad Romanos. ca. viii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e341" source="http://scta.info/resource/rom8_14@1-9">Qui cumque spi
               <lb ed="#P" n="64"/>ritu dei agnntur hii sunt filii dei.</quote>
            </p>  
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e348">
               <lb ed="#P" n="65"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e380">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro. viii. epistola. xxvi.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="66"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e352">Quos superna pertegunt felices aduersarios 
               <lb ed="#P" n="67"/>habere non possunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-d1e358">
               <lb ed="#P" n="68"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Rd1e392">Prouerbium vulgare</ref><!--This whole section is very odd. I can not fnd a corresponding verse nor can I make it make good Latin-->
               <lb ed="#P" n="69"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de2065-Qd1e362">A chi dio vuol bene dormendo liuiene
               <lb ed="#P" n="70"/>A chi dio vuol male glitogle il semno
               <lb ed="#P" n="71"/>A chi dio vuol male lepecore il mordano</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
